# Resume Quality Auditor Skill (Claude Code)

Performs a rigorous 16-part data quality audit on Resume Council pipeline outputs.

## Capabilities
- Multi-agent orchestration for deep verification.
- Semantic diffing of resume tailored versions.
- Rendering integrity checks for premium HTML templates.
- AI slop and "cope" language detection.

## Instructions
When asked to audit a resume run, follow the 16-part protocol defined in the Resume Quality Auditor specification. Use sub-agents to parallelize the inspection of markdown, JSON, HTML, and PDF artifacts.
